   <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>topic</keyword>&gt; element is the top-level DITA element for
a single-subject topic or article. Other top-level DITA elements that are
more content-specific are &lt;<keyword>concept</keyword>&gt;, &lt;<keyword>task</keyword>&gt;, and &lt;<keyword>reference</keyword>&gt;.</shortdesc>
